\id PHP - Akawaio New Testament Translation Project 
\h PIRI'PAI 
\toc1 Kareta Paarʉ Nennoko'pʉ Piri'pai Pon Kon Ena' 
\toc2 Piri'pai 
\toc3 Piri'pai 
\mt2 Kareta Paarʉ Nennoko'pʉ 
\mt1 Piri'pai Pon Kon 
\mt2 Ena' 
\imt1 Ekamanin 
\ip \bk Kareta Paarʉ Nennoko'pʉ Piri'pai Pon Kon Ena'\bk* e'menuka'pʉ wapiyaro' Paarʉ nʉ'mʉ'sa'ka'pʉ Yuro' pon kon nono po, Roman amʉ' nono pʉ'kʉ Ma'sitoniya pon. Iye'menuka'pʉ itekare ekamase'na enno'sa' esi koro'tau pariki'si tau, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ewa'noma pɨ' te'san tʉron kon Kʉri'san pe e'nɨ tʉrawasooi ku'nin nan uya imanenpa a'tai mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ennakanin pe enupan nɨto', so'si Piri'pai yawon tau uya isakoropa'pʉ. E'tane si serɨ enno'sa' kareta uya pori' pe e'nɨto' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ enu wannɨ yau e'nɨto' enna'pi'nʉnka, Paarʉ rɨ ken uya Sises Kʉrai apurɨto' ipan pe uya enpoika. 
\ip Inke pʉra iye'to' wenai serɨ tenno'sen kareta e'menuka'pʉ Piri'pai awon kon Kʉri'san amʉ' pɨ' tepori'mato' ekamanin pe i'se te'to' tʉrepato' ike rʉ'pʉ pɨ' tʉpika'tɨnin pe, pɨ'. Mɨrɨ koro'tau si pori' pe tenu kon yau to' e'to' pe to' usewankama namai' tanporo imanenpanin pe te'sen yau mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉmɨrɨ'nokon nɨ nɨrɨ usewankamato' yau. To' ekama'po iya ipan pe Sises eseru mɨ pe te'ku'sen pen kasa to' e'to' pe, amʉre' pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ mɨ pe te'ku'sen pe e'nɨto' esi namai' to' esa' pe. To' emiya'pontɨ'pʉ iya to' uko'manto' Kʉrai pokon pe esi Papa uya wakʉ nonkasa' winon pe, to' neporo'pʉ to' uya apurɨto' winɨ, main, Mosi' winon Esuwerʉ amʉ' iwano' awɨrɨ e'nɨ nʉkupʉnʉ winon pen. Pori' pe e'nɨto' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉusewankamai' pʉra e'nɨto' Papa nʉtʉrʉ'pʉ kamoro Kʉrai pokon pe tʉuko'mansa' pɨ' imenuka iya. 
\ip Serɨ kareta e'ma'kʉi'tɨsa' mɨrɨ pori' pe e'nɨto', enu wannɨ yau e'nɨto', a'samʉtʉ pe tikin nɨ tenai e'nɨto', mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ sa'man annawɨrɨ rɨ Kʉri'san pe e'nɨ uya apurɨto' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ uko'man nɨto' pɨ' iyetʉ'ka. Enpoika iya rɨ nɨrɨ ipan pe Paarʉ uya so'si Piri'pai yawon i'nʉnkato'. 
\iot Iyawon Ekamanin 
\io1 Ekamanin (1:1-11) 
\io1 Ipoirɨ rɨ Paarʉ pɨ' te'ku'sen (1:12-26) 
\io1 Kʉrai yau uko'man nɨto' (1:27—2:18) 
\io1 Temu'ti mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ E'pa'pʉrotai'tas iwano' ekonekan nɨto' (2:19-30) 
\io1 Panaman nɨto' eyaton non mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨsɨ ton namai' (3:1—4:9) 
\io1 Paarʉ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ itonpa ton Piri'pai pon kon (4:10-20) 
\io1 Iu'matʉ (4:21-23) 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Paarʉ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Temu'ti, Sises Kʉrai poitorʉ ton winɨpaino,\x - \xo 1:1 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 16:12\x* 
\p Tanporo wakʉ ton a'samʉtʉ pe so'si epuru ton mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ to' pika'tɨnin nan pokon pe te'san Sises Kʉrai yau Piri'pai yau te'san enakan: 
\p  
\v 2 Wakʉ nonkasa' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉusewankamai' pʉra e'nɨto' nesii ɨyenakan kon pe, Papa, ukʉipʉnʉ kon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Itepuru Sises Kʉrai winɨpaino. 
\s1 Tenki Tato' Mɨrɨ Awonsi'kɨ Ɨpʉreman Nɨto' 
\p  
\v 3 Tenki tapɨtʉ uya Papa pɨ' ɨyenuminkapɨtʉ uya 'nokon kaisarɨ rɨ.  
\v 4 Tanporo ɨpona'nokon ɨpʉrema yau, tɨwɨrɨ rɨ ɨpʉrema pori' pe esii'ma,  
\v 5 apʉne pʉra utonpa pe ɨwesi kon wakʉ itekare yau, iye'sara'tɨ'pʉ si'kɨrɨ serɨ pʉ'kʉ pona rɨ,  
\v 6 serɨ i'tu uya pɨ' kuru rɨ, kʉrɨ wakʉ tʉrawaso piya'tɨnin nʉ'pʉ ayau'nokon uya ikupʉ iu'matʉ pʉ'kʉ pona, Sises Kʉrai uyepʉ weyu pʉ'kʉ pona. 
\p  
\v 7 Iye'to' pe rɨ serɨ kasa e'ku'ai' tanporo ɨpɨ'nokon, apʉne pʉra uyewan yau ɨkupʉ uya 'nokon pɨ', ɨ'rɨ pe rɨ esi yau a'sisa' pe mɨrɨ pe pʉra e'wa'kʉtʉ yau mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ wakʉ itekare meruntɨtanʉkʉ uya yau, tanporo ɨmɨrɨ'nokon uya Papa uya wakʉ nonkasa' eporo upokon pe.  
\v 8 Papa uya tanporo ɨmɨrɨ'nokon i'se e'to' ekama mɨrɨ Kʉrai Sises usi'nʉnkato' ike ke. 
\p  
\v 9 Serɨ serɨ ɨpʉremato': ɨusi'nʉnkato' kon enato' pe miyarɨ rɨ eke pe i'tunin pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ipan pe ennin pe,  
\v 10 mɨrɨ si wakʉ pe te'sen i'tunin pe ɨwesi kon pa, ɨri tato' ipɨ' pe pʉra mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ esuken Kʉrai weyu pʉ'kʉ pona,  
\v 11 ipokena' pe e'nɨto' nepetanʉkʉnʉ ke itarʉ'tɨsa' pe tʉuye'sen Sises Kʉrai poro—eke pe Papa ku'to' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ apurɨpɨ'to' pe. 
\s1 Paarʉ I'sen Uya Miyarɨ Rɨ Wakʉ Itekare Usekama Kupʉ 
\p  
\v 12 I'tu auya'nokon i'se e'ai', utonpa ton, iye'ku'sa' rʉ'pʉ upɨ' uya miyarɨ rɨ wakʉ itekare usekama ku'sa' man.  
\v 13 Mɨrɨ moron nʉ'pʉ pe tensen pe tanporo kopʉna pata'se' erasu ton koro'tawɨrɨ iyenasa' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tanporon kon pona rɨ Kʉrai iwano' pe i'sen yau esi.\x - \xo 1:13 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 28:30\x* 
\v 14 Uya'sisa' wenai tu'ke rɨ tonpa ton pe te'san Itepuru yau, epori'mapɨ'sa' tʉusauro'san pe Papa Maimu pɨ' epiyɨ'kena' pe pʉra mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ enari'mʉra. 
\p  
\v 15 I'nairɨ rɨ iyesi tʉron kon uya Kʉrai ekareei ekama tɨkɨnta kon pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉusakorota kon pe, e'tane tʉron kon uya ekama wakʉ pe kuru nin iteseru esii'ma.  
\v 16 Serɨ pe iwa na'ne' nan uya ikupʉ usi'nʉnkan nɨto' yau, i'tui'ma serɨ ya' e'tʉsa' esi wakʉ itekare wapu pe.  
\v 17 Wapiyaro' kon uya itekare ekama'pʉ Kʉrai pɨ' tiwano' kon pe ɨnku'pai te'to' kon i'napai rɨ pʉra rɨ, ekamʉn ne'nin pe upona a'sisa' pe esi koro'tau.\f + \fr 1:17 \ft Tʉron nɨ ton serɨ iwa pe imenukasa' yau v. 17 esi v. 16 rawɨrɨ.\f* 
\v 18 E'tane, ɨ'rɨ pe ken iyesi? Eke esi mɨrɨ tanporon yau, kasi ye' rɨ eseru wannɨ mɨrɨ pe pʉra i'nairo' yau, Kʉrai ekareei usekamasa'; serɨ wenai nin si pori' pe esi. 
\p Ewai', miyarɨ rɨ epori'man pɨ' esi,  
\v 19 i'tu uya wenai ɨwɨpʉremato' kon winɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ epika'tɨto' esi Sises Kʉrai a'kwarʉ winɨ, serɨ iye'ku'sa' rʉ'pʉ upɨ' esi mɨrɨ upa'kanin pe.\f + \fr 1:19 \fq upa'kanin pe; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq upika'tɨnin pe.\f* 
\v 20 Enurikʉ serɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ e'ku'to' esi epiyɨ'to' pe pʉra, e'tane enari'ke' pʉra e'to' serɨ pe siya rɨ Kʉrai namato' pe upun yau, uko'manto' yau mɨrɨ pe pʉra eri'to' yau.  
\v 21 Apʉne pʉra urɨ pona, uko'man nɨ pe Kʉrai esi, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ eri'nɨ esi eporo pe.  
\v 22 Apʉne pʉra uko'mamʉ pe iyesi yau upun yau rɨ, serɨ esi mɨrɨ miyarɨ rɨ epekena' pe e'tʉrawasoma ta e'kwa pe. Mɨrɨ rɨ e'tane, ɨ'rɨ kuru ken si anʉmʉ uya? I'tu uya pʉra rɨ iyesi!  
\v 23 Ekaraka serɨ asa'ron a'sanau: emo'kapai rɨ esi mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Kʉrai a'kɨrɨ e'to' pe, wakʉ pe kuru rɨ nin;  
\v 24 e'tane miyarɨ rɨ ɨiwano' kon pe kuru upun yau e'to' pe iyesi,  
\v 25 Si'tuyai' rɨ serɨ, si'tuyai' serɨ yau rɨ e'to' esi tukai' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tanporo aya'kɨrɨ'nokon nɨ esi mɨrɨ ikupʉ kon pa mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ pori' pe ɨwesi kon pa apurɨto' auya'nokon yau,  
\v 26 mɨrɨ kasa si urɨ esi ɨpiyau'nokon kanan uya pori' pe ɨkupʉ kon, Kʉrai Sises yau ɨwe'to' kon anʉ'kato' pe urɨ pɨkɨrɨ. 
\p  
\v 27 Ɨ'rɨ rɨ e'ku'tane, ɨiwano' kon pe rɨ iye'to' awɨrɨ Kʉrai ekareei yau e'tɨ'. Mɨrɨ a'tai, uyepʉ ɨyense'na'nokon, mɨrɨ pe pʉra eta uya rɨken ɨpɨ'nokon, urɨ pʉra rɨ iye'tane i'tu uya rɨ mɨrɨ, ɨye'soto'kasa' kon pana' pe tikin nɨ iya'kwarʉ tikin nan ka'pon pe itekare apurɨto' pɨ',  
\v 28 tenari'nʉnse pʉra ɨ'rɨ pɨ' rɨ ɨyewa'nomanin kon nʉkupʉnʉ pɨ'. Serɨ esi mɨrɨ to' uya ento' ipɨ', to' uma'ta ekamanin, ɨmɨrɨ'nokon nin si epika'tɨ tane, Papa winɨ.  
\v 29 Ɨyena'nokon iye'tʉsa' pɨ', Kʉrai iwano' pe apurɨ kon pa rɨken pen, e'tane ɨyekota'mato' kon pe rɨ iyesi itiwano' pe,  
\v 30 mɨrɨ awɨrɨ rɨ sa'ne ɨutɨ kon esi mɨrɨ e'suranman pɨ' uyenta'tʉine' awɨrɨ rɨ, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ serɨ pe eta auya'nokon urɨ rɨ esi e'suranman pɨ'.\x - \xo 1:30 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 16:19-40\x* 
\c 2  
\s1 Kʉrai E'to' Mɨ Pe Te'ku'sen Pe Pʉra Pataka 
\p  
\v 1 Ɨuko'manto' kon Kʉrai yau uya pana' pe ɨku'sa' kon, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ isi'nʉnkato' uya aya'kwarʉ kon ne'sa', mɨrɨpan uya Iya'kwarʉ pokon pe ɨku'sa' kon ɨsi'nʉnkena' pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨsentu'kena' pe ɨtonpa kon amʉ' pokon pe.  
\v 2 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', ipan pe ɨyekama'po uya 'nokon mararon pe pʉra pori' pe uku'tɨ' ɨsi'kaisa rɨ tʉusenuminkai', tʉusi'nʉnkai' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tikin nɨ iya'kwarʉ, tikin nɨ isenuminkato' te'se.  
\v 3 Amʉre' pe rɨ ɨwesi kon pɨ' ɨ'rɨ rɨ kʉ'ku'tʉu mɨrɨ pe pʉra rɨ autaperʉka kon pe rɨ, e'tane se pe rɨ e'ku'tɨ', tʉron kon kupʉi'ma wakʉ pe ɨyentai'nokon.  
\v 4 Akaisarɨ'nokon ɨtonpa kon tense e'tɨ', ɨmɨrɨ'nokon pɨ' rɨken pen. 
\p  
\v 5 Ɨyeseru kon nesii Kʉrai Sises esi'pʉ kasa: 
\q1  
\v 6 I'naino pe kuru rɨ Papa pe te'sen, e'tane 
\q2 Papa kaisa rɨ esi i'se iyesi'pʉ pen, ta'sisen pe, 
\q1  
\v 7 e'tane tanporon nɨ nonka'pʉ iya, 
\q2 i'naino ipoitorʉ pe e'nɨto' anʉmʉ'pʉ iya, 
\q2 ka'pon pe tekonekasa' pɨ'. 
\q1  
\v 8 Ka'pon pe si tʉusene pɨ', 
\q2 se pe rɨ iyena'pʉ 
\q2 mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ uma'tan nɨto' maimu awɨrɨ rɨ iyesi'pʉ—kurusu' po rɨ uma'tan nɨto'! 
\q1  
\v 9 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', Papa uya anʉmʉ'pʉ kakʉi' kuru rɨ 
\q2 mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ itese' ke irepa'pʉ iya, tanporo ese' pe te'sen entaino ke rɨ, 
\q1  
\v 10 mɨrɨ pɨ' Sises ese' pɨ' tanporon ese'mu ton e'sekunka, 
\q2 Epʉn yawon kon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ non pon kon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ non o'non kon,\f + \fr 2:10 \fq non o'no: \ft Iyeri'sa' kon esi ewarupɨ yau uko'man nɨ pɨ' tukai' usenuminkan nɨto' esi.\f* 
\q1  
\v 11 mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tanporon kon uya ekama Sises Kʉrai esi Itepuru pe, 
\q2 Papa Ikʉipʉnʉ ku'to' eke pe kupʉ pe.\x - \xo 2:11 \xt Aisaya 45:23 (LXX)\x* 
\s1 E'wei'tɨn Sirikɨ Amʉ' Kasa 
\p  
\v 12 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', utonpa ton nʉ'kwɨ, main awɨron kon pe rɨ ɨwe'pɨtʉ kon—moro rɨken esi pɨ' pen, e'tane serɨ pe mɨrɨ entai ipʉra esi pɨ'—ɨyepika'tɨto' kon tʉrawasooi pɨ' rɨ e'tɨ' ɨyetʉipɨtʉ kon, e'tɨtɨtɨ'ka pe rɨ,  
\v 13 apʉne pʉra Papa e'tʉrawasoma ayau'nokon iku'nin pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨnku'pai ɨwesi kon pa ipori'manin pe te'sen. 
\p  
\v 14 Tanporon nɨ iku'tɨ' tepatakai' pʉra mɨrɨ pe pʉra te'sei'pɨ'se pʉra,  
\v 15 mɨrɨ si wakʉ pe, ɨri pʉra mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ esuken ɨwesi kon pa Papa munkɨ pe, tʉuko'mansan pe ɨri yau mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨri ton koro'tau tʉma'takʉʉi ke pʉra. To' koro'tau e'wei'tɨtɨ' sirikɨ amʉ' te'wei'tɨsan kasa ka' yau;\x - \xo 2:15 \xt Isu'taronomi 32:5\x* 
\v 16 to' pɨ' uko'man nɨto' ekareei ekama auya'nokon koro'tau. Mɨrɨ kupʉ auya'nokon yau, utapurɨto' esi mɨrɨ Kʉrai weyu a'tai, apʉne pʉra enpoika iya mɨrɨ utʉrawasooi, unkuu'pʉ e'sa' pʉra iyesi notʉn pe.  
\v 17 E'tane ɨ'rɨ pe pʉra rɨ iyesi use'man nɨto' ike pe te'sen tensisen kasa rɨ use'man nɨto' pona rɨ e'ma tane apurɨto' auya'nokon winɨ, pori' pe rɨ esi epori'ma rɨ tanporo aya'kɨrɨ'nokon.  
\v 18 Mɨrɨ kasa rɨ marɨ pori' pe e'tɨ' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ epori'matɨ' upokon pe. 
\s1 Temu'ti Mɨrɨ Awonsi'kɨ E'pa'pʉrotai'tas 
\p  
\v 19 Itepuru Sises yau, e'kupʉ kuru rɨ serɨ Temu'ti enno'to' pe uya serɨ pe'ne rɨ ɨpiya'nokon, pori' pe e'to' pe ɨyekareei kon etasa' uya a'tai.  
\v 20 Ɨnʉ' pʉra rɨ man iwaraino, i'napai rɨ ɨuko'manto' kon ennin.  
\v 21 Tanporon kon nɨ nin esi tiwano' kon pɨ', Sises Kʉrai iwano' pɨ' pen nɨ nin.  
\v 22 Temu'ti i'tusa' auya'nokon nɨ, imu esi tʉkʉipʉnʉ a'kɨrɨ kasa uya'kɨrɨ iye'sa' wakʉ itekare tʉrawasooi yau.  
\v 23 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', enno'to' pe uya kuru rɨ e'kupʉ serɨ inke pʉra ɨ'rɨ pe rɨ te'sen e'kupʉ ensa' uya a'tai upɨ'.  
\v 24 Urɨ nɨrɨ esi uyenu yau Itepuru yau serɨ pe rɨ urɨ rɨ utɨto' oton pɨ'. 
\p  
\v 25 E'tane usenuminka serɨ E'pa'pʉrotai'tas na'po pɨ' ɨpiya'nokon, utonpa, uya'kɨrɨ te'tʉrawasomasen, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ uisakon pe soisa pe te'sen, amaimu kon nɨrɨ ekamanin, ɨnennoko'pʉ kon i'se e'to' ennin pe.  
\v 26 Apʉne pʉra ɨyenpai'nokon iyesi mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ika'nɨ' pʉra rɨ iyesi, apʉne pʉra takuru'ke iyesi tawon etasa' auya'nokon pɨ'.  
\v 27 I'nai rɨ, takuru'ke iyesi'pʉ, ima'taiwa'pʉ rɨ. E'tane Papa usentu'ma'pʉ ipɨ', kʉrɨ rɨ pɨ' rɨken pen, urɨ pɨ' rɨ nɨrɨ, pokoi pe e'to' tonpa'tɨ pe rɨ iyesi namai' pokoi ke.  
\v 28 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', miyarɨ rɨ mɨrɨ pɨ' ɨnenno'pai esi ensa' auya'nokon a'tai kanan, ɨyepori'ma kon pa mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ usewankamato' pʉra iye'to' pe.  
\v 29 Mereutanʉ'tɨi' Itepuru yau ipan pe, pori' pe esii'ma, ka'pon amʉ' kʉrɨ rɨ waraino kon mʉnamatʉi',  
\v 30 apʉne pʉra ima'taiwa'pʉ rɨ Kʉrai tʉrawasooi pɨ', ɨsɨ rɨ tʉuma'tato' annau rɨ iyena'pʉ upika'tɨnin pe, ɨmɨrɨ'nokon uya ikupʉ poken pʉra iyesi pɨ'. 
\c 3  
\s1 Pun Kupʉ Pen En Yau 
\p  
\v 1 Iu'matʉ pe rɨ si, utonpa ton, Itepuru pɨ' pori' pe e'tɨ'! Mɨrɨ rʉ'pʉ rɨ marɨ menuka uya ɨyena'nokon uya uyanpokʉmato' pʉra man, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨserasu kon pe iyesi. 
\p  
\v 2 Kamo pero amʉ' enei'ma e'tɨ', kamo ka'pon amʉ' makoi ku'nin nan, kamo pun ma'tanʉ'nin nan.  
\v 3 Apʉne pʉra urɨ'nokon kamoro iputurʉkasa' ton, tʉwɨpʉremasan Papa A'kwarʉ awɨrɨ, Kʉrai Sises apurɨto' ipɨkɨrɨ, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ pun kupʉ pɨ' tenu kon yau te'san pen—  
\v 4 urɨ rɨ mɨrɨ wenai uyenu yau esi tato' uya e'tane. 
\p Ɨnʉ' rɨ usenuminka yau mɨrɨ wenai ipun esi uyenu yau tukai', urɨ man mɨrɨ entai rɨ:  
\v 5 itun pi'pɨ iputurʉkasa' 8 pan wʉi a'tai, ka'pon amʉ' Esuwerʉ pon kon pe, Pensiman rʉko' pe, Ipuru amʉ' pe; main, Mosi' winon awɨrɨ, Pari'si pe;\x - \xo 3:5 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 23:6; 26:5; Ron 11:1\x* 
\v 6 ipan pe ɨnku'paino pe e'to' pɨ', so'si amʉ' kota'ma pɨ'; Mosi' nʉnonka'pʉ awɨrɨ e'nɨ pɨ', ima'takʉʉi pʉra.\x - \xo 3:6 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 8:3; 22:4; 26:9-11\x* 
\p  
\v 7 E'tane si tɨ, ɨ'rɨ rɨ eporo uya mɨrɨ winɨ tasa' uya e'tane, eposa' uya pʉra iyesi tukai' ito'ka'nʉkʉ uya Kʉrai uriya' rɨ si.  
\v 8 Mɨrɨ entai, tanporon to'ka'nʉkʉ uya teposen pe pʉra rɨ, i'tu tanporo eke pe te'sen entai Kʉrai Sises uyepuru i'tuto' esi, kʉrɨ rɨ uriya' tanporon nɨ nonka'pʉ uya serɨ. Eno'masa' pe rɨ ene uya, Kʉrai epoto' pe uya  
\v 9 kʉrɨ rɨ yau iye'seposa' pe e'to' pe, uiwano' pe ipoken e'to' pe pen main winɨ tʉuye'sen, e'tane mɨ Kʉrai apurɨto' poro—wakʉ ipokena' Papa winon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ apurɨto' winɨ tʉuye'sen.  
\v 10 Kʉrai ɨni'tupai esi mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ iye'mʉ'sa'ka'pʉ meruntɨrʉ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ita'kɨrɨ iyekota'ma'pʉ yau esi, ikasa rɨ ena iyeri'to' yau,  
\v 11 mɨrɨ pɨ' si mɨrɨ kasa rɨ iye'mʉ'sa'ka'pʉ terikʉ'pʉ apai eponin pe e'to' pe. 
\s1 Teposen Winɨkʉi' Utɨn 
\p  
\v 12 Tanporo serɨ ton anʉnka'sa' uya pen, mɨrɨ pe pʉra wakʉ pe ekonekaka'sa' pen, e'tane uta'kwarʉka uta'sito' pe Kʉrai Sises uya uya'sisa' na'ne' pɨ'.  
\v 13 Utonpa ton, uta'sika'sa' pʉra iwa rɨ man ipɨ' e'tane tikin nan kupʉ uya, uye'ma'pʉ ta' te'sen tʉpu'tɨka'nʉ'se mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ sa'man pe uta'kwarʉka urawɨrɨ te'sen ekare pɨ',  
\v 14 teposen ekare pɨ' uta'kwarʉka epoto' pe uya, Papa uya ukɨ'masa' na'ne' ipona Epʉn winɨkʉi' Kʉrai Sises awɨrɨ. 
\p  
\v 15 Tanporo urɨ'nokon iyakʉ'pʉsa' ton uya ento' esi. Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉron nɨ airɨ usauro'ai'ne' pɨ' tʉron nɨ pe ɨusenuminka kon yau, mɨrɨ rɨ kanan enpoika Papa uya ɨyena'nokon.  
\v 16 Utɨnpai'nokon eporo'pʉ uya'nokon na'ne' awɨrɨ rɨken. 
\p  
\v 17 Tʉron kon a'kɨrɨ e'sara'tɨtɨ' unkupʉ'pʉ kupʉ pɨ' utonpa ton, kamo ina nʉkupʉ'pʉ kasa tʉuko'mansan entɨ'.\x - \xo 3:17 \xt 1 Koren 4:16; 11:1\x* 
\v 18 Apʉne pʉra wapiya tapɨtʉ pɨ' rɨ e'sa' ɨpɨ'nokon, serɨ pe kanan si takapʉ uya akaramʉi'ma, tu'kan kon nɨ uko'mamʉ Kʉrai kurusukuui eyaton pe.  
\v 19 To' utɨto' ya' esi uma'tan nɨto', to' e'to' itese' pɨ' esi to' ewan, to' e'to' eke pe esi to' epiyɨ'to' yau. To' usenuminkato' esi non eseru pɨ' rɨ.  
\v 20 E'tane urɨ'nokon esi Epʉn pon kon pe, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ enuri'nɨ'nokon itenupɨkɨrɨ pika'tɨnin Itepuru Sises Kʉrai uyepʉ mɨrɨ winɨ,  
\v 21 imeruntɨrʉ uya tanporon nɨ ena iyo'koi' emapu'tɨ, sepan nɨ upun kon ensima iya, a'kwa tʉpun kasa iye'to' pe. 
\c 4  
\p  
\v 1 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', utonpa ton, ɨmɨrɨ'nokon uni'nʉnkanʉ ton mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ itenupɨkɨrɨ e'to' ton, pori' pe uku'nin nan mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ uyarʉko kʉron ton, mɨrɨ kasa kuru meruntɨ pe Itepuru yau te'mʉ'sa'kai' e'tɨ', utonpa ton nʉ'kwɨ! 
\s1 Panaman Nɨto' 
\p  
\v 2 Iyotiya mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Sinti'ki, ɨyekama'po uya 'nokon ipan pe ɨseseru yau ɨwesi kon pa Itepuru yau.  
\v 3 Ɨmɨrɨ, uisakon pe te'tʉrawasomasen\f + \fr 4:3 \fq uisakon pe te'tʉrawasomasen; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq awɨron Sisikos\ft —itese'.\f* ekama'po uya pʉsamoro uri'sami'si amʉ' ipika'tɨkɨ uya'kɨrɨ wakʉ itekare pɨ' ita'sisa' kon, Kʉremen pokon pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉron kon e'tʉrawasoma tonpa ton, to' ese' e'menukapɨ'sa' na'ne' uko'man nɨto' karetaai pɨ'. 
\p  
\v 4 Pori' pe Itepuru yau e'tɨ' tɨwɨrɨ rɨ. Takapʉ uya kanan: Pori' pe e'tɨ'!  
\v 5 Tɨwɨ tanporon kon pɨ' ɨsɨ pe pʉra ɨwe'to' nʉsenei. A'ko pe Itepuru man.  
\v 6 Ɨ'rɨ pɨ' rɨ kɨsewankamatʉu, e'tane tanporon yau rɨ, ɨwɨpʉrema kon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ekama'po auya'nokon yau, ɨyepori'ma kon pe, ɨnesakʉnʉ kon itʉtɨ' Papa ena'.  
\v 7 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉusewankamai' pʉra e'nɨto' Papa iwano', tanporon nɨ ito'ka'nʉ'to' entaino rɨ esi ɨyewan kon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨusenuminkato' kon erasu pe Kʉrai Sises yau. 
\p  
\v 8 Iu'matʉ pe rɨ, utonpa ton, ɨ'rɨ rɨ i'nai rɨ na'ne', ɨ'rɨ rɨ tese ke na'ne', ɨ'rɨ rɨ ipokena', ɨ'rɨ rɨ esukenan, ɨ'rɨ rɨ wakʉ pe oso tato' ipɨ' pe na'ne', ɨ'rɨ rɨ en yau na'ne'—ɨ'rɨ rɨ wakʉ pe kuru rɨ na'ne' mɨrɨ pe pʉra tapurɨpɨ'sen ye' pe, mɨrɨ waraino ton pɨ' kuru ɨsenuminkatɨ'.  
\v 9 Ɨ'rɨ rɨ uwinɨpai ɨusenupa'pʉ kon pɨ' mɨrɨ pe pʉra ananʉmʉ'pʉ kon mɨrɨ pe pʉra ɨneta'pʉ kon mɨrɨ pe pʉra ɨnene'pʉ kon uyau—iku'tɨ' si. Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ nin si Papa usewankaman nɨto' pʉn nɨ e'to' pe ɨpiyau'nokon. 
\s1 Tenki Ta Itʉsa' Ton Pɨ' 
\p  
\v 10 Eke pe kuru epori'mayai' Itepuru yau, emennʉ'pʉ rɨ upɨ' ɨusewankamato' kon enpoikasa' auya'nokon pɨ'. I'nairɨ rɨ sa'ne, pena upɨ' ɨusewankama'pʉ kon, e'tane enpoikato' auya'nokon a'tai pʉra iyesi'pʉ.  
\v 11 Ekota'ma pɨ' ta uya pen serɨ, apʉne pʉra isenupasa' urɨ ɨ'rɨ pe rɨ e'nɨ yau pori' pe te'sen pe.  
\v 12 I'tu uya rɨ ekota'man nɨto', mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ i'tu uya rɨ eke pe itesa' pe e'nɨto'. Usenupasa' man mɨrɨ yau e'nɨto' eseru pɨ' pori' pe te'sen pe ti'tui' pʉra rɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tanporon yau rɨ e'nɨto' pɨ', eke pe rɨ tenta'nai' mɨrɨ pe pʉra iwan pe rɨ e'nɨto' yau; eke pe rɨ itesa' pe e'nɨto' yau mɨrɨ pe pʉra ipʉra e'nɨto' yau.  
\v 13 I'tu uya rɨ, tanporon nɨ kupʉ, imeruntɨrʉ ke. 
\p  
\v 14 E'tane wakʉ pe rɨ upika'tɨ pɨ' ɨwe'sa' kon man ekamʉn yau esi koro'tau.  
\v 15 Mɨrɨ tonpa'tɨ pe, ɨmɨrɨ'nokon Piri'pai pon kon ni'tuyai'ne' kasa rɨ, pena wakʉ itekare to'ka'nʉkʉ pɨ' ɨyena kon yau Ma'sitoniya poi utɨ a'tai, tikin nan nɨ so'si uya upika'tɨsa' pʉra iyesi urɨ tʉrepai' i'se e'to' ke, ɨmɨrɨ'nokon nɨken;\x - \xo 4:15 \xt 2 Koren 11:9\x* 
\v 16 Tesaroni'ka po rɨ kanan esi a'tai i'se e'to' enno'pɨtʉ pɨ' ɨwe'pɨtʉ'pʉ kon.\x - \xo 4:16 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 17:1\x* 
\v 17 Urepato' auya'nokon, enupɨkɨrɨ esi pen, e'tane ɨnkupʉ'pʉ kon epe'pʉ eporo auya'nokon enupɨkɨrɨ nin esi.  
\v 18 Tanporo kuru rɨ, iye'to' entai rɨ ɨwinɨpai'nokon eposa' uya man, serɨ kanan si epoka'sa' uya E'pa'pʉrotai'tas winɨ ɨnennoko'pʉ kon urepato' auya'nokon ike. A'po'nan ikɨtun tʉtʉsen pe iyesi, tanʉnsen ye' use'man nɨto' pe iyesi Papa pori'manin pe iyesi.\x - \xo 4:18 \xt E'sotas 29:18\x* 
\v 19 Mɨrɨ pɨ' nin si Papa itese' pɨ' e'to' uya tanporon nɨ i'se ɨwe'to' kon ke ɨrepa kon mɨrɨ eke pe rɨ itesa' pe te'to' ke Kʉrai Sises yawɨrɨ. 
\p  
\v 20 Papa itese' pɨ' e'nɨto' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ukʉipʉnʉ kon iwano' pe eke pe iku'to' nesii inke rɨ, inke rɨ te'sen pe. Amen. 
\s1 Iu'matʉ Pe Miyarɨ Ta 
\p  
\v 21 “Miyarɨ,” ka'tɨ' Kʉrai Sises yau wakʉ ton pɨ'. Utonpa kon amʉ' upiyawon kon, “Miyarɨ,” tato' ennoko pɨ' man.  
\v 22 Tanporo wakʉ ton, “Miyarɨ,” tato' ennoko pɨ' man ɨyena'nokon, kamoro kuru Sisa iwʉ' tawon kon. 
\p  
\v 23 Wakʉ nonkasa' Itepuru Sises Kʉrai iwano' nesii aya'kwarʉ kon piyau. Amen.\f + \fr 4:23 \ft Tʉron nɨ ton imenukasa' ton yau \fq Amen \ft pʉra iyesi.\f*